name: mebull
description: - Clone and rename folder `$ git clone git@github.com:dented-academy/express-ejs-starter.git your_project_name_here` - Find and rename all instance of `your_project_name_here` to your project name - Create a `.env` file   ```txt   COOKIE_SECRET=put_something_random_here   ``` - Run `$ npm install` - Run `$ npx sequelize-cli init` - Run `$ npx sequelize-cli db:create` - Run `$ git remote remove origin` - Create a new repo and add the repo ssh link to remote - Run `$ git push origin master`

scripts.gen-models: sequelize-auto -o './models/schema' -d mebull_development -h localhost -p 5432 -e postgres --cf l --sg true
